room_title: Escape room "Knucklehead Garage" by Sleuth Escape Rooms in Kearney
room_description: Grandma Gert has done it again!  A little too eager to get her car back from repairs, she's run it through the wall at Knucklehead Garage!  Larry, the manager, has managed to hide the keys away from her, but can't seem to remember where he put them!  Can you help the crew at Knucklehead find the keys before Grannie does?
